         <div type="translation">
            <ab>His father to Adamas, greeting. Do not omit to send home news how things go with you, what they are like, and to exhibit prudence so that I shall not have to come up about this same affair. For Aniketos the agent of Eubios the archiphulakites ï¿½ (Here the papyrus is illegible). (Addressed on the verso) To Adamas.</ab>
